        </div>
        <div class="right-side">
          <p>I wanted to raise money to help these girls and at the same time do something fun to make more people aware of their situation.</p>
          <p>I thought about my life as a child... in the Argan Oil forests of Morocco near to where I grew up live some strange goats who like to climb trees.</p>
          <p>I loved goats and still doâ€¦ their long silly tongues, weird rectangular eyes and crazy screams are super funny.</p>
          <p>So I set out to create a squawking rubber toy that represents this legendary animal. One that I could sell to raise money and help these girls get a better education...</p>
          <p>Thatâ€™s when Gabi the Goat and Gabi the Goat was born.</p>
        </div>
