          <p>I had a way to raise money with Gabi the Goat so now all I needed was a way to use the money to help the girls get the education they deserve.</p>
          <p>This is where Education For All (EFA) Morocco comes in. EFA Morocco is a non-profit that builds and runs boarding houses for girls who want to continue their education.</p>
          <p>The boarding houses allow the girls to live closer to school and everything is provided to them for free so money is no longer an issue.</p>
          <p>With Gabi Iâ€™m now on a mission:<br/>To use the power of goats to provide girls in rural Morocco with a better education.</p>
